item.title: Portfolio
item.description: Portfolio I have worked on a number of fantastic projects in the past couple of years. Here’s some cool ones, Advancing Prostate Cancer Detection Prostate Cancer is one of the most common types of cancer among men. Around 1 in 7 men in Ireland will be diagnosed with Prostate Cancer and about 3,665 men are diagnosed every year. This work aims to develop Machine Learning Models to identify the Pathological Grade of Prostate Cancer and key clinical biomarkers.
